<body>
    <h1>T5 - Requirement Analysis Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"d11788fa1cf3" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-=
1.Introduction">1. Introduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"0aaf3dcffa90" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.1Purpo=
se">1.1 Purpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"3d3ea58d78d5">This document defines the functional and non-f=
unctional requirements of the 3-Tier AWS Serverless Web Application integra=
ted with <strong>GitHub Actions for CI/CD automation</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"aa08317f0cad">The system implements a scalable serverless ar=
chitecture on AWS and automates backend deployment using a GitHub Actions w=
orkflow.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"2c063ac7c680" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-Intended=
Audience:">Intended Audience:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"9e8ca67a-936c-40d6-8f35-018d60870291">
<li local-id=3D"eb3f0072-d3f2-4361-b66e-061c4937d17b">
<p local-id=3D"286f4d6fb7f0">CTO</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"29b425a2-2875-44a9-8b0c-1735680c2bee">
<p local-id=3D"4a99ed778bc7">Solution Architects</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"68ae4050-1f1b-4461-ad04-399b1aea9b3e">
<p local-id=3D"b501cd98d370">DevOps Engineers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"45522d3d-b33e-4071-9092-e414655393ef">
<p local-id=3D"043a6168dc3f">Developers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ae93e016-ea1f-4664-a42d-d7c5e47416e4">
<p local-id=3D"3dad52d1c1e2">Cloud Architects</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0d91f10b-f15c-42ea-bf3a-2c8a134f1c34">
<p local-id=3D"af8519ac27db">Project Stakeholders</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ac20803ed919">This document establishes system requirements,=
 CI/CD workflow, deployment automation standards, and operational guideline=
s.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"8c7c9c67-6f1c-4821-82f2-ddec265c98e7">
<h2 local-id=3D"490f9701053c" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.2Scope=
">1.2 Scope</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"ad6515b48391" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-Included=
inScope:">Included in Scope:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"e54107ea-04a7-486c-83d1-73c11954b8f6">
<li local-id=3D"260032f1-f82f-4e3c-8cb1-fb81df31236d">
<p local-id=3D"c197dc5fc052">Frontend hosted on Amazon S3</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ce8f1722-1e45-4586-8fae-13807e69edf5">
<p local-id=3D"2730e71fa50c">Backend hosted on AWS Lambda (Node.js + Expres=
s)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d798bce7-2518-48de-a2ce-df4ee9008888">
<p local-id=3D"46483b09a33b">API Gateway integration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7f33202c-652a-4d88-881e-b2199b570c65">
<p local-id=3D"011f89724407">Amazon RDS (MySQL) database</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ee26b151-5e4d-43ee-8c0b-c7c08671501b">
<p local-id=3D"7f5769406cdf">VPC and Security Groups configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"26f26639-da08-4c79-a1dc-bb93473d401a">
<p local-id=3D"dbe4fb45d775">IAM role configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bf0e302d-1537-469b-b461-5f99def8a8d4">
<p local-id=3D"bb8ffe55f4f9">CloudWatch logging and monitoring</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"34814421-c75d-4012-8333-2c9829628b5f">
<p local-id=3D"f52175823de2">GitHub Actions-based CI/CD pipeline</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d1a30793-df85-4046-833b-cc6b626d57a4">
<p local-id=3D"3ec8f1fe09f1">Automated backend build and deployment process=
</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"3b2b4fdc77fa" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-NotInclu=
ded:">Not Included:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"2ed6de4a-2c55-40b7-95f4-5ba6693a11ab">
<li local-id=3D"30f9869e-bc94-4831-bff6-3a7f40266757">
<p local-id=3D"698e5f618e13">Multi-region deployment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b7034c29-80dd-482a-a18a-c35f5bc55577">
<p local-id=3D"e08f88406cde">Kubernetes-based orchestration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"22c67187-b171-46c9-9855-e01243d38479">
<p local-id=3D"516ec31243d0">Advanced canary or blue-green deployments</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"e85b10a9-bfbf-4d2f-a001-0f1847de0b01">
<p local-id=3D"95c1ba8b71f6">Identity federation (OAuth/SAML)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c0a19340-c195-49f7-98e2-d372f768f60c">
<p local-id=3D"679749bc0771">Multi-environment staging (Dev/Test/Prod separ=
ation)</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"6431349f-e9ac-4d88-8f5d-00b86924d917">
