<hr local-id=3D"1db82150-ef6d-4f0e-bd90-7ade9882f92c">
<h2 local-id=3D"97980b0a66af" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.5Overv=
iew">1.5 Overview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"ee8c94607d20">This document includes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"1b23f695-540e-4935-b4aa-4afc1d937a3d">
<li local-id=3D"c70f0b4d-3c19-4cea-a1de-de649b68ba0f">
<p local-id=3D"928984321538">Project overview</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4d28d979-718e-49a9-a322-c31b835da113">
<p local-id=3D"2fc034f806d6">Functional requirements</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d073527a-6bec-42db-a925-bf271eca5774">
<p local-id=3D"3b2bb4397260">CI/CD automation workflow</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ae70205d-83f9-4f47-8edf-19c9ed0c4261">
<p local-id=3D"8de377e4f4f2">Non-functional requirements</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3609cb32-1847-499f-ba13-3a4e872645f1">
<p local-id=3D"10fa4bb148cf">Risk analysis</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6a78e0e2-9aec-4cf7-bfca-8101efb265a4">
<p local-id=3D"7a89b84d6418">Security controls</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"42f9a494-74b9-4f6f-bff6-fee903c04867">
<p local-id=3D"0e2355ee0656">Business alignment</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"ce6b5419-c122-45f2-bcff-db3e0effa33f">
<h1 local-id=3D"fab7fd835d94" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.Projec=
tOverview">2. Project Overview</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"f6fd9cbfc0bf" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.1Proje=
ctObjectives">2.1 Project Objectives</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"f19f67ff-51fb-4a7e-916b-924e754ba58e">
<li local-id=3D"8b94b690-33ca-4632-93cf-ae97c8541083">
<p local-id=3D"94936718060f">Implement a scalable 3-tier serverless archite=
cture</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"37b90c15-bc8a-4e06-bfd6-e4efa80360ac">
<p local-id=3D"188164950cc9">Automate backend deployment using GitHub Actio=
ns</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7d9278d8-4a68-4e7a-b193-709478cc090c">
<p local-id=3D"7f8213fa4d34">Eliminate manual ZIP uploads to Lambda</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"4fb2f86c-6c43-4b9a-b7dd-dce967811abd">
<p local-id=3D"e797a5a5ab42">Reduce deployment errors</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"48e18375-b6c8-4e71-8fa0-7b814211a178">
<p local-id=3D"9fa75bcdce9c">Enable faster release cycles</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bbcdb815-1eb7-44ac-88ac-f98826ae3780">
<p local-id=3D"c9c83fbdd9c5">Maintain secure and reliable infrastructure</p=
></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"618daf59-1060-4d87-bfbc-0c9fec3b16b7">
<h2 local-id=3D"91fd1daa7982" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.2Busin=
essGoals">2.2 Business Goals</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"1d7ee4ba-4da3-4b09-aefd-d5bb783e69cf">
<li local-id=3D"b1a24695-6bd9-4ff6-93a8-083d3fe40314">
<p local-id=3D"d123946eabb5">Improve deployment speed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a038f8b3-fdac-4a9f-a317-712832a27eb8">
<p local-id=3D"1f129aed9cb0">Reduce operational risk</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"af5700a4-68da-4c76-84ae-d2e3af36ffa1">
<p local-id=3D"eee5e33aba55">Enable repeatable deployments</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"634301cc-b71e-4d48-b366-354dfebf09b1">
<p local-id=3D"d7d76262f117">Improve system reliability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"51d333af-a6d3-4ad6-9067-6bac14f1ef86">
<p local-id=3D"107f2b12dfd4">Support scalable cloud-native architecture</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"10d86cef-fdc2-41d9-b1fc-8140d3129e2c">
<h2 local-id=3D"62c1a7801e91" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.3Backg=
round">2.3 Background</h2>
<p local-id=3D"eb4fd12bd1c2">Previously, backend deployments were performed=
 manually using ZIP uploads to AWS Lambda.</p>
<p local-id=3D"1fcb4175aaad">To improve DevOps maturity and deployment reli=
ability, <strong>GitHub Actions was integrated</strong> to automate:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"cdb2c83a-7aae-4633-93c5-9d2f239d85e8">
<li local-id=3D"b269d14a-b125-4b7e-be6d-b77b2c28958e">
<p local-id=3D"f89fc957e1dc">Code retrieval from repository</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"98dfc5f3-e5f5-4e36-8fce-2eecf70e9c12">
<p local-id=3D"0fb264c69b29">Dependency installation (npm install)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cf84d88c-56d5-4e5f-9fba-deeb0db0a7da">
<p local-id=3D"7d4172519c2a">Packaging of Lambda function</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d8288525-981a-4e90-bb54-7f68b14d4c34">
<p local-id=3D"b641f35e673c">Deployment using AWS CLI</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b29766d7-ae4b-40ff-8075-e46bbef40caa">
<p local-id=3D"380bc655b2da">API Gateway redeployment (if required)</p></li=
>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"67d5444a6f69">This eliminates manual intervention and ensure=
s traceable, repeatable deployments.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"83084eea-ec03-4aef-b260-f799689ed1dd">
<h2 local-id=3D"6edd10d0ccb7" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.4Const=
raints">2.4 Constraints</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"88a39cf7-34b7-4f46-9834-393ec2ba2749">
<li local-id=3D"f6e4649f-7a0b-4225-9394-79867aef47ff">
<p local-id=3D"167993d64de9">Single AWS region deployment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"517718fc-7fb1-482f-9649-e1ba42334fce">
<p local-id=3D"fc74d8890395">Budget-limited infrastructure</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"49be78bf-66f4-4a6d-ac66-0cf73250551d">
<p local-id=3D"2db31624d1ea">Basic CI/CD pipeline (no multi-stage approval =
workflow)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"725bf5b3-f714-4d55-b910-c6a5072b2cad">
<p local-id=3D"479e43835113">Serverless-only backend architecture</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"718a015b-fa90-438a-93f5-e49704f0c75e">
<p local-id=3D"cdcecb452598">Single development environment</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"1f1e61ce-535d-4bc0-8215-6ceac8c6a7b2">
<h1 local-id=3D"a8c4a54f88a4" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.Functi=
onalRequirements">3. Functional Requirements</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"8da1665b-cb42-407d-aa44-5af7cbbedc23">
<h2 local-id=3D"967ccb7fbc1a" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.1UseCa=
seDiagram">3.1 Use Case Diagram</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"a943b67742cc" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-Actors:"=
>Actors:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"6b9f1f5a-ab4d-4e06-8fde-d282a5022d32">
<li local-id=3D"0653d0b9-0e9d-4b86-a41d-134b0c24dd4f">
<p local-id=3D"6dceb4e8080d">End User</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4f515850-0846-4b60-97bc-9cf450e5d88d">
<p local-id=3D"605ae51f8afa">Developer</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5eb41e91-cb54-4739-b4eb-6157b95e75d3">
<p local-id=3D"89867c1c8788">GitHub Actions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0233ae92-6baa-4cb0-9186-d5bce3368686">
<p local-id=3D"3f85a943501e">AWS Infrastructure</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"8967848a82df" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-MainUseC=
ases:">Main Use Cases:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"b518a859-882d-49b5-934c-c68f382c68f2">
<li local-id=3D"3476fae4-6bd7-4d9f-a7cc-e3cd392fad17">
<p local-id=3D"f8eee60745d0">Access Web Application</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e8ba62e9-3f64-4fd7-9fc3-fff6d2cc410f">
<p local-id=3D"c80f23df5a6e">Create / Read / Update / Delete Tutorial</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"eb58c9c8-8403-4537-a113-03254ae55692">
<p local-id=3D"3c6706450adf">Push Code to GitHub</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0ce47c1f-7d3f-4d6b-9ff3-9494294232db">
<p local-id=3D"8bdf8b376d1c">Trigger GitHub Actions Workflow</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c56cf4c4-9d69-4d0d-b234-db205e7c4e99">
<p local-id=3D"cdeec8e7056d">Deploy Backend Automatically</p></li>
</ul><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper c=
onfluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image ima=
ge-center" alt=3D"Untitled Diagram.drawio (2)-20260309-182334.png" width=3D=
"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"d3f68779dd37d398c3290d529dcad797e6b2189adf459=
92f4f505f5949bbf768" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/do=
wnload/attachments/1798176777/Untitled%20Diagram.drawio%20(2)-20260309-1823=
34.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1773080676005&amp;cacheVersion=3D=
1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"472" data-width=3D"966" data-unresolved-comm=
ent-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1841660379" data-linked-resource=
