<hr local-id=3D"255e30f5-d4fe-451c-9996-bbfd86d9aaaa">
<h1 local-id=3D"b8ffe7bd552f" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2UseCa=
ses">3.2 Use Cases</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"f45bf3b2-509a-44be-9ba9-85fed7d6d926">
<h2 local-id=3D"bdcdb67b0703" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2.1Use=
Case1:AccessWebApplication">3.2.1 Use Case 1: Access Web Application</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"b754ffb677e0" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-Descript=
ion:">Description:</h3>
<p local-id=3D"c640a89c0c34">User accesses frontend hosted on Amazon S3.</p=
>
<h3 local-id=3D"155ce77ccb18" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-Flow:">F=
low:</h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"b39b86c2-0d2d-4325-b15f-89310e0ceb97">
<li local-id=3D"616c83e1-2559-433e-b94c-8db981d9bc00">
<p local-id=3D"7edc2668679c">User enters S3 website URL</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e1cb1df6-62e7-403f-a260-93d7aadbc2ef">
<p local-id=3D"9d444aabe716">S3 serves static frontend files</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0d42dc3c-42c6-453c-8cf4-5f191ed122c6">
<p local-id=3D"a7e13bb21191">React UI loads in browser</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"2c0fdb1c-7f28-4373-8fba-e4a1e861d794">
<h2 local-id=3D"acdc8a10e8fe" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2.2Use=
Case2:CRUDOperations">3.2.2 Use Case 2: CRUD Operations</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"dda7218ce65f" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-Descript=
ion:.1">Description:</h3>
<p local-id=3D"bc673fc33a50">User interacts with backend APIs through the f=
rontend application.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"e31c40e39d92" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-Flow:.1"=
>Flow:</h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"35f79128-3895-47df-9958-ddb23ac2f406">
<li local-id=3D"7b280b57-7242-4153-97ca-c3a1863f3b36">
<p local-id=3D"84d81c38e331">Frontend sends HTTP request</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"32456fb8-d566-4f10-ad4a-ad5a60d17c5b">
<p local-id=3D"a05ce020b3c4">API Gateway receives request</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"768a5f7e-dda9-487c-adc3-21cd25255554">
<p local-id=3D"38acf1f98277">Lambda executes business logic</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e86cdb73-44b4-404b-9de8-b3c3a761be2e">
<p local-id=3D"c97ce17b3f11">Lambda reads/writes data to Amazon RDS</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"f6b36660-f0d5-475c-9318-8c698f52ed4c">
<p local-id=3D"0397934b3855">JSON response returned</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"aba65e4a-2f52-499e-b18d-96e52fc9a172">
<p local-id=3D"4eb74056e670">UI updates dynamically</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"cde8268c-47d5-4e18-bea4-f38f2334a905">
<h2 local-id=3D"8dc5b1a53b0c" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2.3Use=
Case3:CodeDeploymentviaGitHubActions">3.2.3 Use Case 3: Code Deployment via=
 GitHub Actions</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"09daac200f8b" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-Descript=
ion:.2">Description:</h3>
<p local-id=3D"cb6664bb8568">Developer pushes code to the GitHub repository=
, triggering automated backend deployment via GitHub Actions.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"24ad7eac4476" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-Actors:.=
1">Actors:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"f263cd82-680e-45a9-9041-6c6e59d3bff1">
<li local-id=3D"026f18a9-064a-486b-8492-75a9a448c7fc">
<p local-id=3D"14272cfe0733">Developer</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b337dc91-d97d-4df9-8591-b62d10f7fd7a">
<p local-id=3D"519b7512cc4f">GitHub Actions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1c764a67-5f58-4972-9615-afb531cf1436">
<p local-id=3D"ba4ed0cc1cf1">AWS Infrastructure</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"9ed2fce0-b59a-4fc9-be8c-20593b0599b5">
<h3 local-id=3D"e00609f69799" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-Precondi=
tions:">Preconditions:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"ef0a1929-a29d-4aa3-8ec8-75bd526db268">
<li local-id=3D"8a7a950b-7356-4cf4-9f60-d3c2dd22ae3b">
<p local-id=3D"6065ba2443db">GitHub Actions workflow configured</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1f8f8009-c3cc-4124-8d02-01546ea322ad">
<p local-id=3D"7c4793ff0afd">AWS credentials stored securely as GitHub Secr=
ets</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"45dd8639-6a98-4f48-bdea-21d732b6f6f6">
<p local-id=3D"12fb8b342677">Lambda IAM execution role properly configured<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"62f89b5c-a3b8-4805-8eba-bce80f4875d2">
<p local-id=3D"e68210c21285">Repository integrated with GitHub Actions</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"7ca62c77-6add-4eb6-b3a3-85fa12948c5d">
<h3 local-id=3D"b8f98c3caba8" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-Postcond=
itions:">Postconditions:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"9c0c9ffb-36c5-4c77-9f0c-0f4f041362fe">
<li local-id=3D"29d7ce5e-98f0-45c4-adeb-50e1a51c09bd">
<p local-id=3D"2c0f8b2cb0fc">Lambda function updated automatically</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"61bd924a-1a21-40b3-93a3-3c7dd7dd6bdb">
<p local-id=3D"3cb892c017d8">API Gateway redeployed if required</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"29272c56-d82a-4c0a-a9a8-1ef8be07e3a8">
<p local-id=3D"83eee04c5cf6">CloudWatch logs updated</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dd17c753-3a38-4313-a7ea-6cb6b58b672a">
<p local-id=3D"ec48b596a86c">Application reflects latest backend changes</p=
></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d2e5a6f5-5df0-4ea1-a2db-7685a0507d57">
<h3 local-id=3D"22b47007f510" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-FlowofEv=
ents:">Flow of Events:</h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"40f1179c-2c4c-4bca-818e-4012958a3b52">
<li local-id=3D"a8fcb400-cda8-4945-91b1-3016c44213fe">
<p local-id=3D"f523f59587fe">Developer pushes code to GitHub</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"22f72e8c-20aa-4f68-a4d4-f63572c5b395">
<p local-id=3D"98d32a9cff3f">GitHub Actions detects repository change</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"aba02f3b-9e7c-4ebd-84a3-54d9a27b410a">
<p local-id=3D"8076713329c0">Workflow pulls latest source code</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"016d8392-7f77-4936-99b7-38dc0e74fdf0">
<p local-id=3D"a85c3829df1b">Dependencies installed using npm install</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"ce804924-1ad0-4c94-8f22-a7f740c3db06">
<p local-id=3D"9b797d22c3bb">Deployment package created</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e001cc06-cd75-48da-82bd-b94a1c05b083">
<p local-id=3D"5fe1f218a49d">AWS CLI or Serverless Framework updates Lambda=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"992d37d2-0538-43df-a96b-448c23cec823">
<p local-id=3D"d8c44f39899e">API Gateway redeployed (if configured)</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"1ada1bcc-2b30-4d06-8795-1d8713592d11">
<p local-id=3D"365a87e5b03b">Workflow marked successful</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"348a13a8-fe34-49b9-af5f-5c1a42c7294a">
<p local-id=3D"d2af09d40770">CloudWatch logs updated</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"ccce5a5b-f1b4-415a-ab05-123deb69d884">
<h3 local-id=3D"4fff85830353" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-Alternat=
iveFlow:">Alternative Flow:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"71552716-08ff-4536-83e2-e1c6704351e6">
<li local-id=3D"24006146-7ad7-4fe2-812f-168647f59038">
<p local-id=3D"9474f923c7c6">If build fails =E2=86=92 Deployment aborted</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"3ae8162a-182f-4366-8aeb-67cc556c2be1">
<p local-id=3D"8e70b310bf16">If packaging fails =E2=86=92 Workflow marked f=
ailed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"90b8c878-f695-4074-9449-13522705f940">
<p local-id=3D"246250990429">If AWS CLI fails =E2=86=92 Job marked failed</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0b620646-43b8-4a7e-ada8-aef85e777fda">
<p local-id=3D"f14aa56313c9">If IAM permissions incorrect =E2=86=92 Deploym=
ent terminated</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"c446d1a5-00a8-412a-aead-3598ff0957da">
<h1 local-id=3D"e2fab01deec4" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.Non-Fu=
nctionalRequirements">4. Non-Functional Requirements</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"d4546749-33a1-4afc-8c6c-25454fc9dadf">
<h2 local-id=3D"757b0635f1d7" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.1Perfo=
rmanceRequirements">4.1 Performance Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"597e1aed-8117-45d9-b00d-d778766806bd">
<li local-id=3D"7bcb1636-edb9-4274-9f4b-502e825105a3">
<p local-id=3D"1ce09e389ccd">API response time &lt; 2 seconds</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"95fba095-6b4f-40c5-a0f9-d7976deff1a5">
<p local-id=3D"6343e96abcca">GitHub Actions workflow completes within defin=
ed build window</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9e66e134-0277-45ad-a139-29f824475f34">
<p local-id=3D"5e6f78ad6f68">Lambda auto-scales under concurrent load</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"8a3381f5-4cca-4a18-bca9-3227773247c6">
<p local-id=3D"f39679d42a89">RDS handles expected transaction volume</p></l=
i>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d2e6fd5c-bbf9-4a20-94d8-e5b1e677b2d9">
<h2 local-id=3D"5765ec4d0e53" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.2Secur=
ityRequirements">4.2 Security Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"220a557e-10f2-407f-966c-67cf6570906c">
<li local-id=3D"f9d09710-f2b7-447e-a8a5-060cfc837eae">
<p local-id=3D"201a1fe23a6d">IAM least privilege access</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bcd4f156-705d-4b94-8a05-6e4ad1935a62">
<p local-id=3D"c5992d03d213">AWS credentials stored securely in GitHub Secr=
ets</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"487dbef8-88a6-43ef-8246-91032a2cd753">
<p local-id=3D"d527a48d83a2">No hardcoded credentials</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b9aa2f0f-6aab-4e42-b3f2-23a9d5a4c621">
<p local-id=3D"6310c1151a1a">VPC-isolated RDS instance</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c2481a29-4e7c-47d1-af4f-1554fb5225df">
<p local-id=3D"03e5ad130e25">Security group-based DB access control</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"868cf6ef-2631-4f10-8ec2-f31966260fb9">
<p local-id=3D"a8ccaf17c97a">HTTPS API endpoints</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"0714ea43-8cce-4cae-ad7d-9c57b162b9f7">
<h2 local-id=3D"f0536d40ae23" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.3Usabi=
lityRequirements">4.3 Usability Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"9ec88fcc-8928-4406-832b-55f2c9fbc3a5">
<li local-id=3D"59c17365-d7d3-45d5-9a50-0f8b6505fffa">
<p local-id=3D"4467aeb3aab2">Responsive frontend UI</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ca385ede-4792-4116-964f-64538d9a435c">
<p local-id=3D"0befeddd3193">Clear API response messages</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"21233a47-eda7-48c3-b79f-57eb928e3abc">
<p local-id=3D"a1c5b5acf08c">Deployment logs accessible via GitHub Actions<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6fc4c00d-61a5-43d6-b3a5-dd8ab858cc4f">
<p local-id=3D"92efc6926d56">CloudWatch logs available for debugging</p></l=
i>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"ddeaa4ba-30f9-43ee-b993-b62585e8a971">
<h2 local-id=3D"9a4f640aa6b8" id=3D"T5-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.4Relia=
bilityRequirements">4.4 Reliability Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"8610580a-ddfa-40d9-b79e-9cc19750a90f">
<li local-id=3D"d2ed30e9-277a-4d97-b690-3b6fb68bc3d6">
<p local-id=3D"0bdf82b63a3a">Automated build reduces human error</p></li>
